name: X Marks the Spot
description:
Insights from the Dreaming pool - This is it ! this is where it's at, the treasure is here. Look no further this is the spot. This is where you are now this moment and in every moment. This is it, you are here now you are nowhere else only here and now. In the future you will be here now and in the past you were there then. The Treasure is here in this moment of being alive. You may be dealing with the consequences of what has gone before and so be strong and deal with them. Find whatever will help you best and learn, transmute and transform. X marks the spot of being alive.


The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
